Class JobDeleteMessageReceived

  • java.lang.Object
    • Job
      • com.palomamobile.android.sdk.core.qos.BaseRetryPolicyAwareJob<Void>
        • com.palomamobile.android.sdk.message.JobDeleteMessageReceived

  • public class JobDeleteMessageReceived
extends BaseRetryPolicyAwareJob<Void>
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageService.deleteMessageReceived(String, long, long) Delete a received message identified by messageId. Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageReceivedDeleted on the IEventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
